title: Draft Recap - Rounds 2 & 3
itunes:title: Draft Recap - Rounds 2 & 3
description:
Bucky Brooks, Rhett Lewis and Lance Zierlein are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys emphasize how good the execution of the virtual draft has been. Next, the trio give their favorite picks of Rounds 2 and 3 (5:10). Then, the guys state the most surprising picks from the night (18:08). To wrap up the show, they look at the top storylines from the draft (39:09).
